data.title: Thunderbird Hills
data.text: Thunderbird Hills is a family owned 36-hole golf facility located on the beautiful banks of the Huron River. We are literally minutes from the best roller coaster park in the world, Cedar Point, the largest indoor water park in the country, Kalahari Resort, some of the nicest beaches in Ohio, and the Lake Erie Islands. Our public golf courses are the finest in the area including the Sandusky Ohio golf courses, Huron, Norwalk, Vermilion and other surrounding communities. Both 18 hole courses are always in great condition, with interesting layouts and challenging greens
